After 5 hours straight of slave labor over the character and member 
pages (and despite certain people that will remain unmentioned asking 
me if I'm done every few seconds), I have finished the chars and 
members pages! They are now up and viewable at http://nbwrpg.com

If your character isn't on there and you are 100% sure that you 
submitted him/her/it via the form, inform me about it. If your 
character isn't up there and you have not submitted him/her/it via 
the form, submit him/her/it!

Other than that, take a quick look. I also updated the events page. 
Oh, and if anyone leads a faction whose base isn't listem on the 
events page, email me with the location. Thanx!

I GTG, but I'll be back soon.


Oh, and as KSL requested, lets pause the battle at the CF till he has 
a chance to post.
